OL,7,FA father and son deliberately drove a
OL,8,Fvan into a group of people and killed
OL,9,Fa 60-year-old man who was carried on
OL,10,Fthe bonnet for 150m before he fell, a
OL,11,Fjury was told.
OL,13,FShaun Breeze, 28, called his father
OL,14,FMartin Breeze, 56, for help after he
OL,15,Ftried to intimidate a group who were
OL,16,Fon a night out, Teesside Crown Court
OL,17,Fheard on Monday 15 July.
