OL,3,CFather and son drove van at group and
OL,4,Ckilled man, 60, out of revenge - jury
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FThe court was told the pair were
OL,8,Fmotivated by revenge when they mowed
OL,9,Fdown four people, narrowly avoiding a
OL,10,Ffifth.
OL,12,FBrian Darby, 60, was killed after he
OL,13,Fwas struck by the Citroen Berlingo
OL,14,Fdriven by Martin Breeze on a footpath
OL,15,Fin Myton Way, Ingleby Barwick,
OL,16,FTeesside, around 11.30pm on 2 February.
