OL,3,CFather and son drove van at group and
OL,4,Ckilled man, 60, out of revenge - jury
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FThe prosecution said both were guilty
OL,8,Fof murder as Martin Breeze was at the
OL,9,Fwheel and Shaun Breeze encouraged and
OL,10,Fassisted him by identifying the
OL,11,Ftargets.
OL,13,FThey both face alternative counts of
OL,14,Fmanslaughter, attempted murder charges
OL,15,Fwith alternative counts of causing
OL,16,Fgrievous bodily harm with intent, and
OL,17,Fperverting the course of justice by
OL,18,Fclaiming the van had been stolen at
OL,19,Fthe time.
