OL,3,CFather and son drove van at group and
OL,4,Ckilled man, 60, out of revenge - jury
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FShaun and Martin Breeze deny the
OL,8,Fcharges.
OL,10,FNick Dry, prosecuting, said Mr Darby
OL,11,Fhad been out with a group of different
OL,12,Fages at the 3 Rivers Cafe and there
OL,13,Fhad been "no hint of any trouble".
OL,15,FBut as they walked home, they had the
OL,16,F"misfortune to encounter" Shaun Breeze
OL,17,Fwho was on a bike, Mr Dry said.
