OL,3,CFather and son drove van at group and
OL,4,Ckilled man, 60, out of revenge - jury
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FThe friends remonstrated with him when
OL,8,Fhe barged into one of the group and he
OL,9,Ftried to give them the impression he
OL,10,Fhad a knife.
OL,12,FBut refusing to be intimidated, some
OL,13,Fof the group chased him off, only for
OL,14,Fhim to abandon his bike when he
OL,15,Fcollided with someone else.
OL,17,FShaun Breeze then called his father, a
OL,18,Fpainter and decorator, at their home
OL,19,Fin Owls Grove, in Ingleby Barwick, and
OL,20,FMartin Breeze was seen on CCTV driving
OL,21,Foff in his van to collect his son.
