OL,3,CFather and son drove van at group and
OL,4,Ckilled man, 60, out of revenge - jury
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FMr Dry said: "The pair of them had
OL,8,Fonly one thing in mind and that was
OL,9,Frevenge."
OL,11,FShaun Breeze identified the group to
OL,12,Fhis father and Martin Breeze, who was
OL,13,Fstill at the wheel, "made a beeline
OL,14,Ffor them", the prosecution said.
OL,16,FHe left the carriageway, crossed a
OL,17,Fgrass verge and cycle-path and
OL,18,Fdeliberately drove into the group, in
OL,19,Fa moment captured from a distance on
OL,20,FCCTV, jurors were told.
