OL,3,CFather and son drove van at group and
OL,4,Ckilled man, 60, out of revenge - jury
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FMr Darby was carried on the bonnet for
OL,8,F150m before he fell into the opposite
OL,9,Fcarriageway, the court heard.
OL,11,FDespite the efforts of a passing
OL,12,Fdoctor and former trauma nurse, plus
OL,13,Fparamedics who arrived later, he could
OL,14,Fnot be saved.
OL,16,FA woman in the group suffered life-
OL,17,Fthreatening injuries, while two others
OL,18,Fwere also hit, and a fifth escaped "by
OL,19,Fthe barest of margins", the court
OL,20,Fheard.
