OL,3,CFather and son drove van at group and
OL,4,Ckilled man, 60, out of revenge - jury
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FThe Breezes drove off, abandoned the
OL,8,Fvan which was badly damaged at the
OL,9,Ffront and later told police it had
OL,10,Fbeen stolen.
OL,12,FAfter they were arrested on suspicion
OL,13,Fof murder, both continued to deny
OL,14,Fresponsibility, Mr Dry said.
OL,16,F"They used their vehicle as a deadly
OL,17,Fweapon, no less so than were it to
OL,18,Fhave been a knife or firearm when used
OL,19,Fin the manner and with the intent the
OL,20,Fevidence reveals," he said.
